Text:
Sorry Cristo but there have come brand new courses on Math tutor DVD, where Circuit Analysis volume 2 and HP50 calculator tutor are among the latest.

The "complete" Math tutor DVD, is not complete any more. Far from it. But not to say that it is some good lectures there, recommend it heartfully. But I really need Circuit Analysis badly!

The site comes with new courses continuosly. Thanks for the effort anyway.
